---
// src/pages/play.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="How to Play - Werewolves Revenge">
  <main class="container">
    <h1>How to Play & Install</h1>
    <p>Get ready to lie, deceive, and survive. Follow the steps below to install the game.</p>

    <hr />

    <section class="download-section">
      <h2>1. Download the Game</h2>
      <a href="https://your-itch-io-or-steam-link.com" class="download-button">
        Download for Windows (PC)
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="steps-section">
      <h2>2. Installation Guide</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Download the `.zip` file from the link above.</li>
        <li>Extract the contents to a folder on your computer.</li>
        <li>Double-click <code>WerewolvesRevenge.exe</code> to launch the game!</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="rules-summary">
      <h2>3. Core Rules</h2>
      <p>
        The town must work together to deduce who the hidden threats are before night falls, 
        while the wolves attempt to eliminate the townspeople one by one.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Quick temporary styling to make it look decent */
  .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; font-family: sans-serif; }
  .download-button { 
    display: inline-block; background: #e51b1b; color: white; 
    padding: 1rem 2rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px; 
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  .download-button:hover { background: #b31212; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
</style>